Build CMake SDK Toolchain Project
execute the test only when both test_build_tree_toolchain and build_tree_path parameter are set. Set build_tree_path or  test_build_tree_toolchain to blank to skip this test case.
a) in project explorer, create new c/c++ project with Cmake hello world template and Yocto Project SDK CMake Toolchain (alpha) toolchain
b) right click on the project, go to configure and select  "Configure/Configure as Yocto Project CMake project (alpha)"
c) in prompted project properties select Build Tree toolchain profile -> click "apply and close"
d) refresh project explorer tab
e) pin "CDT Global Build Consolse"
f) right click on project -> select "Regenerate CMake build files" , if prompt for "Regenerate CMake Build Files", click "Yes"-> validate toolchain in console .
g) right click on project -> select "Build Project"-> validate toolchain in console.
